 I was pleasantly surprised to read under the Obstacles section, the following
ruling

"Robots may not hop, jump, skip, or fly over obstacles or any portion of the
arena."

One quickly realises that drafting rules for our bots to follow isn't that
easy. Even the definition of a robot is, as you say, *fuzzy*.

Whatever, have fun!

